  "title": "Senior Site Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Providing guidance to subcontractors and the site team on construction design documents and project execution.</p><p>Leading the day-to-day management of construction activities, ensuring project deadlines are met.</p><p> Monitoring and controlling project expenditures to ensure financial accountability.</p><p>Supervising quality assurance processes and enforcing health and safety standards.</p><p>Overseeing the engineering and construction of form tunnels and sprayed concrete chambers.</p><p> Communicating with the site manager and the rest of the site team, and assisting with site organization.</p><p>Maintaining records, site diaries, quality assurance documentation, and reports.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=b80566c7d948205bec6525fda5518d8ef424082d7d05be9c28cdc20256bd1f70JmltdHM9MTc2OTU1ODQwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0dd00340-a0bf-6fcb-0963-1681a1fa6e46&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvYnVpbGRpbmctY29uc3RydWN0aW9uL3Nlbmlvci1zaXRlLWVuZ2luZWVyLXR1bm5lbGluZy13b3Jrcy1ycmVjcnVpdGVyLTM4OTRiZjMzNWE2YWQzOWQ3YzhlNTAwM2JkZTMxNGZi&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=b80566c7d948205bec6525fda5518d8ef424082d7d05be9c28cdc20256bd1f70JmltdHM9MTc2OTU1ODQwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0dd00340-a0bf-6fcb-0963-1681a1fa6e46&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvYnVpbGRpbmctY29uc3RydWN0aW9uL3Nlbmlvci1zaXRlLWVuZ2luZWVyLXR1bm5lbGluZy13b3Jrcy1ycmVjcnVpdGVyLTM4OTRiZjMzNWE2YWQzOWQ3YzhlNTAwM2JkZTMxNGZi&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=b80566c7d948205bec6525fda5518d8ef424082d7d05be9c28cdc20256bd1f70JmltdHM9MTc2OTU1ODQwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=0dd00340-a0bf-6fcb-0963-1681a1fa6e46&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvYnVpbGRpbmctY29uc3RydWN0aW9uL3Nlbmlvci1zaXRlLWVuZ2luZWVyLXR1bm5lbGluZy13b3Jrcy1ycmVjcnVpdGVyLTM4OTRiZjMzNWE2YWQzOWQ3YzhlNTAwM2JkZTMxNGZi&ntb=1\" target=\"_bl